<h2 id="chord-progressions">Chord progressions</h2>

<p>INTRO</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>| Em . . . | x4
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>VERSE (play twice)</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>| Em . . . | Am . . . | B7 . . . | Em .  .  /D |
| C  . . . | G  . . . | C  . . . | G  .  B7  . |
</code></pre></div></div>

<p>CHORUS</p>

<div class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>| G . D/F# . | Em . . /D | C . B7 . | Am . C . |
| G . D/F# . | Em . . /D | C . D  . | G  . . . |
</code></pre></div></div>

